io.openhc.ohc

Class OHC_ui

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.openhc.ohc.OHC_ui

  • public class OHC_ui
extends java.lang.Object
    This is the only activity and entry point for the app. All the different layouts are organised in pages that update the layout being displayed by this activity. Also this activity keeps track of the pages visited, creating a history of visited pages to allow for easy navigation by native Android controls like the back button.
    Author:
    Tobias Schramm
